Package lib.exceptions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NotElementComparableException
    Exception thrown to indicate that an operation requires elements to be comparable, but the provided elements do not meet this requirement.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ElementNotFoundException
    This exception is thrown to indicate that a specific element could not be found during the execution of a custom collection.
    EmptyCollectionException
    The EmptyCollectionException is a custom exception class that is thrown to indicate that a specific operation could not be performed because the custom used collection is empty.
